des:
COFE App (Coffee ordering fast and efficient)

We highly invest in developing a seamless user experience that fulfills all your coffee needs at any given moment.
Our top-notch services and features are precisely designed to perfect your day by making coffee ordering fast and efficient at all times. With our help your daily coffee is made easier to access with an experience worth living and repeating. With COFE App skill for Amazon Alexa, you can place an order, or know the status of your last order.

Sounds exciting? Enable the COFE App Skill for Amazon Alexa to experience the same with COFE App.
To start using the skill, please follow the given instructions.
Enable the skill on the Amazon Alexa App.
Log in with the mobile number registered with COFE App.
Enter the OTP to validate your identity.
Try our services by saying Alexa, open COFE App, and check the nearby branches.

Note: The payment of the items purchased are made from credit card saved in the COFE App profile.

Your order Is Ready. Enjoy your Coffee with COFE App.
